{"tid":1895083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴中西區民政事務專員黃何詠詩涉嫌公職人員行為失當及違反《公務員守則》","createTime":"2020-02-24T10:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T10:48:02.000Z","uid":127448,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7928ed0c2cbb9dea41fd44f9ddbe10b50cf355a7","tid":1895083,"uid":127448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"結局係...<br />\n政府：我唔認同你，所以投訴無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來函檔號 Your Ref.： 傳真 Fax：2882 8149<br />\n本函檔號 Our Ref.： <br />\n 電話 Tel.：2629 0417<br />\n                日期 Date：24.2.2020<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者︰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關投訴事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n                本署接獲你的電郵。你向本署投訴中西區民政事務專員在當區區議會某<br />\n個會議上中途離席，有失當之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n2.              根據《申訴專員條例》第10(1)條，倘若申訴並非由受屈人士親自提<br />\n出，申訴專員不得對申訴展開調查。由於與會人士才是上述事件的受屈人，因此本署<br />\n未能受理由你所作出的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n3.              謹此回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員<br />\n<br />\n（劉浩榮　　　　代行）<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月24日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n先生／女士： <br />\n<br />\n謝謝你的電郵，我獲授權回覆如下。 <br />\n<br />\n政府十分重視區議會的意見，有關部門首長均會親自到區議會聽取意見。警務處處長於1月16日出席中西區區議會的會議，聆聽及回應區議員的提問。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然而，政府不認同中西區區議會針對警方和警務處處長作出的臨時動議。該動議對警方作出不實的指控。政府不認同區議會的做法和動議的立場，故此所有列席的政府人員均離席。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你對事件的關注。         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署署長 <br />\n(吳芷穎 代行)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都等左好耐，你班撚樣諗左咁尻耐就答呢幾隻字<br />\n做政府真係易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2ed56a314cd749869e175e9dd293bf416c7a1f","tid":1895083,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"現有機制行之有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb06d5a2434793d01d0a3bb6e6ae2929ac7334c","tid":1895083,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c8957d0c3bd0747594a89e7f9c0ba6c3da9838","tid":1895083,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b311dc48261fd106f130abbd70f4a4de10de11fa","tid":1895083,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc39096e0a9f33431269f22f3fd72b5f9c868aad","tid":1895083,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"基於乜嘢原因令佢哋覺得對警曱作出不實的指控？ 你應該舉例子問下721、831"},{"pid":"f69c79533f226083202ca5e7f77e2a6e63d8ba27","tid":1895083,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"區議會唔係政府一部分？"},{"pid":"02c7327ee63f6ce1ddb14fffb44c55dc86f3539c","tid":1895083,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c759e58e320da65111b23226db6b5a8a132bb00","tid":1895083,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"唔同意3隻字就可以搞掂<br />\n呢個垃圾政府要黎做乜尻"},{"pid":"d6c821ef288ede4386b5bceaff8564f85cec048d","tid":1895083,"uid":127448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc39096e0a9f33431269f22f3fd72b5f9c868aad","tid":1895083,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"基於乜嘢原因令佢哋覺得對警曱作出不實的指控？ 你應該舉例子問下721、831"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"我都想繼續問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇手足有咩橋應對"},{"pid":"a8f5b81430c9a5dfc18143fd8d1a0d2e74ec626e","tid":1895083,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0b00e48f8a0ca04b9a5f9c443aa5a85f09ca18b","tid":1895083,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"冇理據嘅唔同意 依個所謂政苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4bdf9c96ceeae91a160068e86ad82d45f15690","tid":1895083,"uid":5103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標對每個本土channel：subscibe+㩒鐘仔+share俾10個fd+睇片+留言+like </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土YouTube Channel? (2.1)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886497\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886497</a>"}]}